menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534607\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534607\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ztp1665702759633.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ztp1665702759633.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ztp1665702759633.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ztp1665702759633\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Operation activated by the SAX parser when it encounters external DTD declarations and\n    unrecognized XML entity references. It must return the text or DTD to be substituted at the\n    reference location.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ztp1665702759633_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__codeblock_c1w_1f4_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation RESOLVEENTITY\nparams\n     string PublicID: in\n     string SystemID: in\n     string ResolveIdentity: out\n  endparams\n\nImplement your code here\n\nend; RESOLVEENTITY operation</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__section_mdj_bf4_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d227826e53\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__ul_xdj_cf4_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__li_d48425e1_d48426e1_d48427e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">PublicID</var>—XML entity reference or\n          DTD name </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__li_d48428e1_d48429e1_d48430e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">SystemID</var>—DTD file name or HTTP\n          address </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__li_d48431e1_d48432e1_d48433e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ResolveIdentity</var>—text to be\n          substituted for the XML entity or the contents of the referenced DTD </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__section_pyw_df4_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d227826e80\">XML Entity References</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__p_d137192e1_d137193e1_d137194e1\">XML entities are symbolical names for pieces of XML or\n        DTD that are defined in DTDs using the <code class=\"ph codeph\">!ENTITY</code> or\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">!ENTITIES</code> keywords. Once defined, XML entities can be referenced in an\n        XML document using the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&amp;<var class=\"keyword varname\">xxx</var>;</code> syntax, where\n          <var class=\"keyword varname\">xxx</var> is the name of the entity. When parsed, the parser substitutes the\n        entity.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__p_d137195e1_d137196e1_d137197e1\">However, when the parser encounters an XML entity\n        reference it does not recognize, it activates <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">RESOLVEENTITY</span>. The\n        operation must return the XML or DTD text that the parser should substitute at that\n        position.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__p_d137198e1_d137199e1_d137200e1\">For example, the following XML will causes\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">RESOLVEENTITY</span> to be activated:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__codeblock_a23_gf4_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;abc&gt;\n &amp;def;\n&lt;/abc&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__p_d137201e1_d137202e1_d137203e1\">The operation should return some XML text in the\n          <var class=\"keyword varname\">ResolveIdentity</var> parameter. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__codeblock_htg_hf4_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;def&gt;texttext&lt;/def&gt;\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__p_d137204e1_d137205e1_d137206e1\">The parser then continues as if the XML document\n        contained <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;def&gt;texttext&lt;/def&gt;</code> at the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&amp;def;</code>\n        position.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__section_yq1_3f4_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d227826e138\">DTD Declarations</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__p_d137210e1_d137211e1_d137212e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">RESOLVEENTITY</span> is also activated\n        when a <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;!DOCTYPE name… &gt;</code> declaration refers to an external DTD. In\n        this case, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">RESOLVEENTITY</span> is called with the name as\n          <var class=\"keyword varname\">PublicID</var>, and the DTD file name or <code class=\"ph codeph\">http:</code> address as\n          <var class=\"keyword varname\">SystemID</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ztp1665702759633__p_d137213e1_d137214e1_d137215e1\">The operation must then return the content of the DTD\n        file indicated in <var class=\"keyword varname\">SystemID</var>, or return an empty string. If an empty string\n        is returned, the parser attempts to resolve the system ID itself by treating it as a\n        URI.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534607\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534607\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "RESOLVEENTITY Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Operation activated by the SAX parser when it encounters external DTD declarations and unrecognized XML entity references. It must return the text or DTD to be substituted at the reference location. Explain this code operation RESOLVEENTITY params string PublicID: in string SystemID: in string ResolveIdentity: out endparams Implement your code here end; RESOLVEENTITY operation Copy Parameters PublicID —XML entity reference or DTD name SystemID —DTD file name or HTTP address ResolveIdentity —text to be substituted for the XML entity or the contents of the referenced DTD XML Entity References XML entities are symbolical names for pieces of XML or DTD that are defined in DTDs using the !ENTITY or !ENTITIES keywords. Once defined, XML entities can be referenced in an XML document using the & xxx ; syntax, where xxx is the name of the entity. When parsed, the parser substitutes the entity. However, when the parser encounters an XML entity reference it does not recognize, it activates RESOLVEENTITY . The operation must return the XML or DTD text that the parser should substitute at that position. For example, the following XML will causes RESOLVEENTITY to be activated: <abc> &def; </abc> Copy The operation should return some XML text in the ResolveIdentity parameter. For example: <def>texttext</def> Copy The parser then continues as if the XML document contained <def>texttext</def> at the &def; position. DTD Declarations RESOLVEENTITY is also activated when a <!DOCTYPE name… > declaration refers to an external DTD. In this case, the RESOLVEENTITY is called with the name as PublicID , and the DTD file name or http: address as SystemID . The operation must then return the content of the DTD file indicated in SystemID , or return an empty string. If an empty string is returned, the parser attempts to resolve the system ID itself by treating it as a URI. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}